    "text": [
        "Dear Sir/Madam,",
        "My name is Krunal Gandhi. I am a final year student of Mechanical Engineering. I am writing for the re-issuance of my university ID card.",
        "Last week, I was travelling from university to my home via state transport bus. Unfortunately, I got pickpocketed and I have lost my University identification card & bank credit cards. I have called  concern bank customer care and blocked my credit cards so that they cannot be misused. However, I am worried about my university ID card because  without ,it I am facing many problems. I am not able to issue books from my university library and my final year examination is coming soon, Moreover, I am not able to withdraw the money which my father has sent for my routine expenses.",
        "I request you to provide a letter which is required as per university norms to re-issue my ID card. You can call me on my mobile number or drop a mail for further details required for your record.",
        "I would also like to inform you that such types of incidents are increasing day by day in our town and I strongly recommend taking strict action against thieves. I look forward to hearing from you.",
        "Jai Hind!!!!",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Krunal Gandhi"
